 data-kid=\"173\">02/03/2024 • 14:30</div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[var(--laser-green)]/70 px-2 py-0.5 border border-[var(--laser-green)]/20 rounded group-hover/item:bg-[var(--laser-green)] group-hover/item:text-[var(--ink-black)] transition-all\" data-kid=\"174\">PDF</div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-[var(--pine-teal)]/20 border border-[var(--pine-teal)]/40 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-between hover:border-[var(--laser-green)]/50 transition-colors cursor-pointer group/item\" data-kid=\"175\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"176\">\n                        <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[var(--ink-black)] flex items-center justify-center border border-[var(--pine-teal)]/30 shadow-[inset_0_0_10px_rgba(57,255,20,0.05)]\" data-kid=\"177\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-anchor text-[var(--laser-green)] text-lg\" data-kid=\"178\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-kid=\"179\">\n                            <div class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"180\">Maritime Storm Alert</div>\n                            <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[var(--laser-green)]/40 mt-0.5\" data-kid=\"181\">02/03/2024 • 11:15</div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[var(--laser-green)]/70 px-2 py-0.5 border border-[var(--laser-green)]/20 rounded group-hover/item:bg-[var(--laser-green)] group-hover/item:text-[var(--ink-black)] transition-all\" data-kid=\"182\">XML</div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-[var(--pine-teal)]/20 border border-[var(--pine-teal)]/40 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-between hover:border-[var(--laser-green)]/50 transition-colors cursor-pointer group/item\" data-kid=\"183\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"184\">\n                        <div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[var(--ink-black)] flex items-center justify-center border border-[var(--pine-teal)]/30 shadow-[inset_0_0_10px_rgba(57,255,20,0.05)]\" data-kid=\"185\">\n                            <i class=\"ti ti-leaf text-[var(--laser-green)] text-lg\" data-kid=\"186\"></i>\n                        </div>\n                        <div data-kid=\"187\">\n                            <div class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"188\">Agri-Moisture Map</div>\n                            <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[var(--laser-green)]/40 mt-0.5\" data-kid=\"189\">01/03/2024 • 09:00</div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[var(--laser-green)]/70 px-2 py-0.5 border border-[var(--laser-green)]/20 rounded group-hover/item:bg-[var(--laser-green)] group-hover/item:text-[var(--ink-black)] transition-all\" data-kid=\"190\">CSV</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <button class=\"mt-4 w-full py-2 bg-[var(--laser-green)]/10 border border-[var(--laser-green)]/30 text-[var(--laser-green)] text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[var(--laser-green)] hover:text-[var(--ink-black)] transition-all duration-300\" data-kid=\"191\">\n                View All Archives\n            </button>\n        </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    \n    <footer class=\"h-10 border-t border-[var(--pine-teal)]/30 px-8 flex items-center justify-between bg-[var(--ink-black)] z-10\" data-kid=\"192\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\" data-kid=\"193\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"194\">\n                <div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--laser-green)] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_5px_var(--laser-green)]\" data-kid=\"195\"></div>\n                <span class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40\" data-kid=\"196\">REMOTE_SENSORS: ONLINE</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"197\">\n                <div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--laser-green)] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_5px_var(--laser-green)]\" data-kid=\"198\"></div>\n                <span class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40\" data-kid=\"199\">ENCRYPTION: AES-256</span>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"200\">\n            <span class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[var(--pine-teal)]\" data-kid=\"201\">V3.4.2-STABLE</span>\n            <div class=\"h-3 w-px bg-[var(--pine-teal)]/30\" data-kid=\"202\"></div>\n            <span class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40\" id=\"current-time\" data-kid=\"203\">MAR 02 2024 // 14:42:01</span>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n  </main>\n</div>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"204\"></script>\n<script data-kid=\"205\">\n  // Update time display\n  function updateTime() {\n    const now = new Date();\n    const timeStr = now.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'short', day: '2-digit', year: 'numeric' }).toUpperCase() + \n                    \" // \" + \n                    now.toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour12: false });\n    document.getElementById('current-time').innerText = timeStr;\n  }\n  setInterval(updateTime, 1000);\n  updateTime();\n\n  // Entrance Animations\n  window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n    gsap.from(\"aside\", { x: -100, opacity: 0, duration: 1, ease: \"power4.out\" });\n    gsap.from(\"header\", { y: -50, opacity: 0, duration: 1, delay: 0.2, ease: \"power4.out\" });\n    gsap.from(\".neon-border\", { scale: 0.95, opacity: 0, duration: 1.2, delay: 0.5, ease: \"expo.out\" });\n    gsap.from(\".teal-border\", { y: 20, opacity: 0, duration: 1, stagger: 0.1, delay: 0.8, ease: \"power3.out\" });\n    \n    // Animate Humidity Gauge\n    gsap.to(\"#humidity-gauge\", { \n        strokeDashoffset: 40, \n        duration: 2, \n        delay: 1.5, \n        ease: \"power2.out\" \n    });\n  });\n</script>\n",
