class=\"font-mono text-[8px] text-red-500/40 tracking-widest uppercase\" data-kid=\"123\">ID: ALERT-PRIO-0</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-xs border border-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center\" data-kid=\"124\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-alert-triangle text-red-500 animate-pulse text-lg\" data-kid=\"125\"></i>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <h3 class=\"font-heading text-lg font-bold text-white/90 mb-2 leading-tight uppercase group-hover:text-red-500 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"126\">Assinatura de Gancho Detectada</h3>\n            <p class=\"font-body text-xs text-red-500/70 leading-relaxed flex-1 font-medium brightness-125\" data-kid=\"127\">Possível formação de tornado detectada pelo algoritmo de mesociclone no setor Oeste.</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-between\" data-kid=\"128\">\n              <div class=\"flex flex-col\" data-kid=\"129\">\n                <span class=\"text-red-500 font-mono text-[10px] font-bold\" data-kid=\"130\">V-COUPLET: 45m/s</span>\n                <span class=\"text-red-500/50 font-mono text-[9px]\" data-kid=\"131\">LOCATION: -22.4, -48.2</span>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"bg-red-500 text-white font-mono text-[9px] px-2 py-1 uppercase\" data-kid=\"132\">URGENTE</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"glitch-card group bg-[var(--pine-teal-dark)]/10 border border-[var(--pine-teal)]/20 p-5 flex flex-col h-80 cursor-pointer hover:border-[var(--laser-green)]/40 hover:transition-colors hover:duration-300\" data-kid=\"133\">\n            <div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-4\" data-kid=\"134\">\n              <div class=\"flex flex-col\" data-kid=\"135\">\n                <span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-[var(--laser-green)] bg-[var(--laser-green)]/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 self-start border border-[var(--laser-green)]/20 mb-1 font-bold\" data-kid=\"136\">SAT-GOES-16</span>\n                <span class=\"font-mono text-[8px] text-[var(--pine-teal)]/70 tracking-widest uppercase\" data-kid=\"137\">BAND: WATER VAPOR</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-xs border border-[var(--pine-teal)]/20 flex items-center justify-center\" data-kid=\"138\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-world text-[var(--pine-teal)] text-lg\" data-kid=\"139\"></i>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <h3 class=\"font-heading text-lg font-bold text-white/90 mb-2 leading-tight uppercase group-hover:text-[var(--laser-green)] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"140\">Anomalia de Vapor d'Água</h3>\n            <p class=\"font-body text-xs text-[var(--pine-teal)] leading-relaxed flex-1 font-medium brightness-125\" data-kid=\"141\">Monitoramento de intrusão de ar seco em altos níveis favorecendo ciclogênese.</p>\n            \n            <div class=\"mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-[var(--pine-teal)]/20 flex items-center justify-between\" data-kid=\"142\">\n              <div class=\"flex flex-col text-[var(--pine-teal)] font-mono text-[9px]\" data-kid=\"143\">\n                <span data-kid=\"144\">ORBIT: GEOSTATIONARY</span>\n                <span data-kid=\"145\">FRAME: 12:45Z</span>\n              </div>\n              <i class=\"ti ti-download text-[var(--pine-teal)] hover:text-[var(--laser-green)] cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"146\"></i>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </main>\n\n    \n    <aside class=\"w-96 bg-[var(--ink-black)] border-l border-[var(--pine-teal)]/40 flex flex-col shrink-0 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"147\">\n      \n      \n      <div class=\"h-24 border-b border-[var(--pine-teal)]/30 flex flex-col justify-center px-8\" data-kid=\"148\">\n        <h2 class=\"font-heading text-lg font-bold text-[var(--laser-green)] uppercase tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"149\">Timeline