 class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-red-500 font-bold\" data-kid=\"180\">11:12 UTC</span>\n                <span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-red-500/50\" data-kid=\"181\">CRITICAL</span>\n              </div>\n              <h4 class=\"font-heading font-bold text-white/90 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"182\">Alerta de Cisalhamento RWY 17</h4>\n              <p class=\"font-['IBM_Plex_Sans'] text-xs text-red-500/80 mt-1\" data-kid=\"183\">Microexplosão (Microburst) identificada por sensores de solo.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"relative pl-12 group !mt-24\" data-kid=\"184\">\n            <div class=\"absolute left-[3.5px] top-0.5 w-6 h-6 -ml-3 bg-[var(--ink-black)] border border-[var(--pine-teal)]/40 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center z-10\" data-kid=\"185\">\n              <div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[var(--pine-teal)]/40 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"186\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex flex-col opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\" data-kid=\"187\">\n              <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-1.5\" data-kid=\"188\">\n                <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[var(--pine-teal)] font-bold\" data-kid=\"189\">10:45 UTC</span>\n                <span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-[var(--pine-teal)]\" data-kid=\"190\">ΔT: 1h 50m</span>\n              </div>\n              <h4 class=\"font-heading font-bold text-white/90 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide\" data-kid=\"191\">Relatório Marítimo S-02</h4>\n              <p class=\"font-['IBM_Plex_Sans'] text-xs text-[var(--pine-teal)] mt-1\" data-kid=\"192\">Boia oceanográfica S-02 reportando altura de onda em declínio.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"mt-auto border-t border-[var(--pine-teal)]/30 p-6 bg-[var(--pine-teal-dark)]/10\" data-kid=\"193\">\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6\" data-kid=\"194\">\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\" data-kid=\"195\">\n            <span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-[var(--pine-teal)] uppercase font-bold\" data-kid=\"196\">Signal Strength</span>\n            <span class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-[var(--laser-green)] tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"197\">94.2 <span class=\"text-[10px] font-mono\" data-kid=\"198\">dBm</span></span>\n            <div class=\"w-full bg-[var(--pine-teal)]/20 h-1 mt-1 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"199\">\n              <div class=\"bg-[var(--laser-green)] h-full w-[94%] shadow-[0_0_8px_var(--laser-green)]\" data-kid=\"200\"></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\" data-kid=\"201\">\n            <span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-[var(--pine-teal)] uppercase font-bold\" data-kid=\"202\">Process Load</span>\n            <span class=\"font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"203\">12.8 <span class=\"text-[10px] font-mono opacity-50\" data-kid=\"204\">TFL</span></span>\n            <div class=\"w-full bg-[var(--pine-teal)]/20 h-1 mt-1 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"205\">\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-400 h-full w-[45%] shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(96,165,250,0.5)]\" data-kid=\"206\"></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-span-2 flex items-center justify-between mt-2 pt-4 border-t border-[var(--pine-teal)]/10\" data-kid=\"207\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"208\">\n            <div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--laser-green)]\" data-kid=\"209\"></div>\n            <span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-[var(--pine-teal)] uppercase\" data-kid=\"210\">Master Clock Sync</span>\n          </div>\n          <i class=\"ti ti-refresh text-[var(--pine-teal)] cursor-pointer hover:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-500\" data-kid=\"211\"></i>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </aside>\n\n  </div>\n\n  \n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont/tabler-icons.min.css\" data-kid=\"212\">\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"213\"></script>\n  <script data-kid=\"214\">\n    // Live Clock Update\n    function updateClock() {\n      const now = new Date();\n      const timeStr = now.toISOString().split('T')[1].split('.')[0] + ' UTC';\n      const clockElement = document.getElementById('live-clock');\n      if (clockElement) clockElement.textContent = timeStr;\n    }\n    setInterval(updateClock, 1000);\n    updateClock();\n\n    // GSAP Animations\n    window.addEventListener('load', () => {\n      // Fade in main elements\n      gsap.from('main, aside', {\n        opacity: 0,\n        y: 20,\n        duration: 0.8,\n        stagger: 0.2,\n        ease: 'power3.out'\n      });\n\n      // Card entrance animation\n      gsap.from('.glitch-card', {\n        opacity: 0,\n        scale: 0.95,\n        duration: 0.6,\n        stagger: 0.1,\n        ease: 'back.out(1.2)',\n        delay: 0.5\n      });\n\n      // Left nav icons staggered\n      gsap.from('nav i', {\n        x: -20,\n        opacity: 0,\n        duration: 0.4,\n        stagger: 0.1,\n        ease: 'power2.out',\n        delay: 0.2\n      });\n    });\n\n    // Filter switching (UI only for now)\n    document.querySelectorAll('.filter-tab').forEach(tab => {\n      tab.addEventListener('click', () => {\n        document.querySelectorAll('.filter-tab').forEach(t => {\n          t.classList.remove('bg-[var(--laser-green)]', 'text-[var(--ink-black)]');\n          t.classList.add('border-[var(--pine-teal)]/40', 'text-[var(--pine-teal)]');\n        });\n        tab.classList.remove('border-[var(--pine-teal)]/40', 'text-[var(--pine-teal)]');\n        tab.classList.add('bg-[var(--laser-green)]', 'text-[var(--ink-black)]');\n      });\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n",
